    <p style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:#374151;" class="mb-3">What this means in practice:</p>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="check-card">
        <span class="check-icon"><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i></span>
        <p>Ingests designs from your existing tools — no rebuild</p>
